Test automation framework using Selenium WebDriver with Java, 
TestNG ,Maven and Cucumber, following Page Object Model Design Pattern
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. This project demonstrates POM framework and how it can be used 
   in selenium to automate any application. TestNG is used as test framework.
   
2. For reports different options are made available:
    A. Extent report : PritamSharma_prob01/test-output/Extent.html
    B. TestNG reports: PritamSharma_prob01/test-output/index.html
    C. Cucumber reports : PritamSharma_prob01/test-outout/index.html

3. For failed cases, screenshot can be found in ritamSharma_prob01\screenShots folder.


5. To run the tests use the following maven command:
     mvn clean test
	 
   OR
   testng.xml file directly can be used to run the test cases
   
   OR 	
   Using PritamSharma_prob01/src/main/java/MyRunner/TestRunner.java class
    
	 
6. Logs can be found in PritamSharma_prob01/application.log.

7. Tests Data parameterization is done using Cucumber.

8. Global properties are added to file in PritamSharma_prob01/src/main/java/com/qa/config/config.properties,
    which contains browser name, URL etc.
